data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem has just been beautifully upgraded with fresh paint throughout, giving it a crisp and modern feel. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the spacious living area, dining space, and kitchen, making it perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing you with ample space to create your own oasis. Whether you're looking to set up a cozy reading nook or a home office, these rooms have all the flexibility you need. One of the standout features of this home is the fenced backyard. Imagine enjoying sunny afternoons in your own private outdoor haven. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends or simply relaxing with a cup of coffee, this backyard offers the perfect backdrop. Situated in a prime location, this home offers both convenience and tranquility. You'll have easy access to local amenities, shopping centers, and dining options, while still enjoying the peaceful ambiance of the neighborhood. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home.
